{"tid":2354683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"質疑武肺疫苗無效影片被下架　顧小培再發文指輝瑞臨床試驗「粗糙」　讚揚中国科興「十分厲害」","createTime":"2021-01-05T15:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T16:13:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"813dcad7b6079702807b887239b67af73494ac0c","tid":2354683,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:47:41.000Z","msg":"「灼見名家」上月中在 Youtube 發布，由香港生物科技研究員顧小培，分析武漢肺炎疫苗的短片，指疫苗「完全沒有保護作用」，長遠更會導致肝腎衰竭。港大微生物學系臨床助理教授薛達 (Siddharth Sridhar) 事後反駁，批評顧的言論是「偽科學」。「灼見名家」社長文灼非證實，影片今日被 Youtube 以「內容不當」下架，已提出上訴。顧小培晚上亦發文，反駁薛達的言論是嚴重指控。文灼非則指，影片是學術討論，又表示暫時未有計劃控告薛達。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/質疑武肺疫苗無效影片被下架-顧小培再發文指輝瑞臨床試驗-粗糙-讚揚中國科興-十分厲害/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%AD%A6%E8%82%BA%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E7%84%A1%E6%95%88%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6-%E9%A1%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%9F%B9%E5%86%8D%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87%E6%8C%87%E8%BC%9D%E7%91%9E%E8%87%A8%E5%BA%8A%E8%A9%A6%E9%A9%97-%E7%B2%97%E7%B3%99-%E8%AE%9A%E6%8F%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88-%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E5%8E%B2%E5%AE%B3%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=d4aa41c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%AD%A6%E8%82%BA%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E7%84%A1%E6%95%88%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6-%E9%A1%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%9F%B9%E5%86%8D%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87%E6%8C%87%E8%BC%9D%E7%91%9E%E8%87%A8%E5%BA%8A%E8%A9%A6%E9%A9%97-%E7%B2%97%E7%B3%99-%E8%AE%9A%E6%8F%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88-%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E5%8E%B2%E5%AE%B3%2F&h=14221ed3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/質疑武肺疫苗無效影片被下架-顧小培再發文指輝瑞臨床試驗-粗糙-讚揚中國科興-十分厲害/</a>"},{"pid":"b09ba9a680612159ffc1a72e6fc9ce94e5cdfe51","tid":2354683,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T16:13:56.000Z","msg":"點架？點先昆到支那廢老同藍屍用支那貨？<img src=\"/assets/face